OL,3,CMPs vote to remove conditional
OL,4,Cimmunity for Troubles' crimes from
OL,5,CLegacy Act
OL,7,FMPs have voted to scrap the
OL,8,Fcontroversial "conditional immunity"
OL,9,Fclause from the previous Conservative
OL,10,Fgovernment's legacy act, ending the
OL,11,Fpause on prosecutions for Troubles-era
OL,12,Fcrimes.
OL,14,FAs it currently stands, the Legacy Act
OL,15,Foffers immunity from prosecution to
OL,16,Fanyone accused of crimes during the
OL,17,FTroubles in Northern Ireland if they
OL,18,Fprovide information to a truth
OL,19,Frecovery body.
