OL,7,FHowever, the High Court in Belfast
OL,8,Fruled parts of the Act were
OL,9,Fincompatible with the European
OL,10,FConvention on Human Rights in 2024.
OL,12,FWhile the Legacy Act was approved in
OL,13,F2023, it was not enacted.
OL,15,FThe then-Conservative government began
OL,16,Fthe process of appealing against the
OL,17,FHigh Court decision, but this was
OL,18,Fdropped by Labour ministers after the
OL,19,F2024 general election.
