OL,3,CMPs vote to remove conditional
OL,4,Cimmunity for Troubles' crimes from
OL,5,CLegacy Act
OL,7,FMore than 3,500 people died during 30
OL,8,Fyears of bloodshed and bombings known
OL,9,Fas the Troubles, which began in
OL,10,FJanuary 1969 when the UK government
OL,11,Fsent troops to Northern Ireland.
OL,13,FSpeaking in the Commons, Northern
OL,14,FIreland Secretary Hilary Benn said the
OL,15,F2023 Legacy Act "fundamentally failed"
OL,16,Fbecause it was incompatible with the
OL,17,FUK's human rights obligations.
OL,19,FFollowing his comments, MPs voted on a
OL,20,FGovernment remedial order to update
OL,21,Fthe legislation.
