OL,5,CLegacy Act
OL,7,FThat vote passed by 373 to 106,
OL,8,Fmajority 267, on Wednesday.
OL,10,FAs a result, the bar on new civil
OL,11,Fclaims over cases from the Troubles
OL,12,Fwill also be removed.
OL,14,FThe remedial order will now go to the
OL,15,FHouse of Lords where it must be
OL,16,Fapproved by peers before the law is
OL,17,Fchanged.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
