OL,7,FMr Benn told MPs: "One of the main
OL,8,Freasons for the failure of the Legacy
OL,9,FAct was its attempt to grant immunity,
OL,10,Fincluding to terrorists who murdered
OL,11,Fin cold blood soldiers and civilians
OL,12,Fin Northern Ireland and in towns and
OL,13,Fcities across England.
OL,15,F"Now, it probably, in fairness, seemed
OL,16,Freassuring to veterans, it was almost
OL,17,Fcertainly reassuring to terrorists who
OL,18,Fhad committed those acts.
OL,20,F"But it was a false promise, and it
OL,21,Fprotected no one."
