OL,7,FHe added: "The Government is clear
OL,8,Fthat these repeals need to happen as
OL,9,Fquickly as possible.
OL,11,F"Why? Because we need to provide
OL,12,Fclarity on immunity to build trust
OL,13,Famongst victims, survivors and indeed
OL,14,Fveterans in the independent commission.
OL,16,F"Because while immunity remains on the
OL,17,Fstatute book, it will be harder for
OL,18,Fthem to obtain the confidence of some
OL,19,Fvictims and survivors."
