OL,7,FAlex Burghart, the shadow Northern
OL,8,FIreland secretary, argued the remedial
OL,9,Forder was a "continuation of the
OL,10,FTroubles by other means" and it was
OL,11,Ftime to draw a line under it.
OL,13,FMr Burghart said he agreed with
OL,14,FConservative MP Lincoln Jopp
OL,15,F(Spelthorne), who described it as a
OL,16,F"proxy war" to "relitigate the
OL,17,Fquestion 'who won?'".
