OL,7,FNorthern Ireland MP and DUP leader
OL,8,FGavin Robinson said: "I believe he is
OL,9,Fbringing this remedial order in
OL,10,Fwrongly. I think he is attaching to
OL,11,Fthese issues a level of undue haste."
OL,13,FMr Robinson also raised concerns over
OL,14,Fthe legacy commission's budget with
OL,15,Fthe "raft of work" it will face as a
OL,16,Fresult of the remedial order.
OL,18,FClaire Hanna, the Social Democratic &
OL,19,FLabour Party MP for Belfast South and
OL,20,FMid Down, said no one had won in the
OL,21,FTroubles.
