OL,7,FShe said: "All of them have lost
OL,8,Fmembers of the family.
OL,10,F"And it's not about people being able
OL,11,Fto draw a line under the past because
OL,12,FMPs in London have told them to."
OL,14,FMs Hanna argued the previous
OL,15,Flegislation was "not about
OL,16,Freconciliation or truth" but "ensuring
OL,17,Fthat Republican and loyalist
OL,18,Fparamilitaries again would have had
OL,19,Ftheir crimes retrospectively
OL,20,Flegalised."
