OL,7,FSir Julian Lewis, the Conservative MP
OL,8,Ffor New Forest East, said: "The truth
OL,9,Fof the matter is that you have to give
OL,10,Fimmunity to everyone or to no one.
OL,12,F"And if the price of giving immunity
OL,13,Fto our servicemen is that we give it
OL,14,Fto terrorists too, then it is a price
OL,15,Fworth paying."
OL,17,FHowever, Sorcha Eastwood, Alliance MP
OL,18,Ffor Lagan Valley, said it was not a
OL,19,Fprice her constituents and "the vast
OL,20,Fmajority of people in Northern
OL,21,FIreland" are willing to pay.
